        <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Sarapion son of Horos. To Horos son of Pathotes 1, likewise 4.  28th (vac.). To Geron son of Pamoun, 50 maria. To Horos son of Akysis, 15. To Horos the donkey-driver, 8. To Sarapion son of Horos for the son of Herak( ) through the son of Ammonios son of Philiskos, 4. Epeiph 13. Share of Psenamounis son of Pathotes 16. I got from Aquila . . .  [- -] 1, Pauni 20</ab>
